### Dataset

```{.r .cell-code}
main_dataset <- main_data_dl |> 
  collapse::fselect(-distribution) |>
  tidyr::unnest_wider(contactPoint, names_sep = "_") |>
  tidyr::unnest_wider(publisher, names_sep = "_") |> 
  collapse::frename(remove_at_symbol) |> 
  remove_all_na()

main_dataset |> 
  purse()
```
